Package com.w2.api.engine.operators

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandSetSequence
    A sequence of RobotCommandSet that will be executed one after another.
    CommandSetSequenceFrame
    The `CommandSetSequenceFrame` object is a container for a single `RobotCommandSet` object and its execution time (in seconds).
    CommandSetSequenceFrameFixed
    The `CommandSetSequenceFrameFixed` object is a container for a single `CommandSetSequenceFrame` object and its associated 'CommandSetSequence' object.
    RobotCommandSet
    `RobotCommandSet` is a collection of 'RobotCommand's to be sent to a robot.
    RobotSensorHistory
    The `RobotSensorHistory` object contains a set of `RobotSensorSet` objects in reverse chronological order.
    RobotSensorSet
    'RobotSensorSet' contains the 'RobotSensor' objects and convenience methods to access these objects.
